OL,3,CInvestigation underway into tonnes of
OL,4,Cillegally dumped rubbish
OL,6,FDiggers move in to begin clearing the
OL,7,Frubbish
OL,9,FCouncil investigators have been
OL,10,Fpicking over the mountain of rubbish
OL,11,Fdumped in the centre of a Lichfield
OL,12,Fstreet to find evidence of who was
OL,13,Fresponsible.
OL,15,FOwing to the scale of the flytipping,
OL,16,Fpolice and the district council have
OL,17,Fsaid they believe the waste has come
OL,18,Ffrom multiple businesses that paid to
OL,19,Fhave it disposed of.
