OL,3,CInvestigation underway into tonnes of
OL,4,Cillegally dumped rubbish
OL,6,FContractors began work to remove the
OL,7,F10-foot-high pile from Watery Lane at
OL,8,Ffirst light on 21 January.
OL,10,FA large lorry is believed to have been
OL,11,Fused to dump the material early on
OL,12,FMonday, blocking Watery Lane in the
OL,13,FCurborough area and leaving the
OL,14,FCurborough Countryside Centre cut off
OL,15,Ffrom cars.
OL,17,FThe council is asking for video
OL,18,Ffootage to track down the flytippers
OL,19,Fwho dumped the mound of building waste.
