OL,3,CInvestigation underway into tonnes of
OL,4,Cillegally dumped rubbish
OL,6,FJack Twomey, Environmental Protection
OL,7,Fand Housing Manager at Lichfield
OL,8,FDistrict Council, said: "I've been
OL,9,Fdoing this job 25 years and I've never
OL,10,Fseen this before.
OL,12,F"We've found quite a few bits of
OL,13,Fevidence they're all leading in one
OL,14,Fdirection so that's giving us quite a
OL,15,Fpositive start.
OL,17,F"So we hope to follow up on those and
OL,18,Fget somewhere with the case."
