OL,3,CInvestigation underway into tonnes of
OL,4,Cillegally dumped rubbish
OL,6,FLichfield District Council said: "Due
OL,7,Fto the scale of the flytipping, we
OL,8,Fimmediately informed the Environment
OL,9,FAgency.
OL,11,F"In the meantime, our environmental
OL,12,Fhealth officers are looking for
OL,13,Fevidence whilst we make arrangements
OL,14,Fto safely remove and dispose of the
OL,15,Fwaste as soon as possible.
OL,17,F"If anyone has information about the
OL,18,Fpeople or vehicles involved, or the
OL,19,Forigin of the waste, please contact us
OL,20,Fon 01543 308000."
